title: Deal orders flags to half-staff to honor fallen soldiers (Georgia Department of Human Services)
text: ( Source : Georgia Department of Human Services ) ATLANTA- Gov. Nathan Deal today ordered flags across Georgia lowered to half-staff in honor of Marine Corps Lance Cpl. Skip Wells of Marietta and Navy Petty Officer 2nd Class Randall Smith of
